name: Fast and Food（HTML5）
description:
Race in three unique routes and deliver your dish to its destination.

Fast and Food! Racing X Restaurant Simulation!

Collect all needed ingredients with your coolest vechile (I mean, a plate). Fast and Food! Power up with your income for non-stop driving action!

Attention! Don't ran your plate over customers, garbage, sh*t and anything not tasty. Play it, and run your own Fast and Food restaurant!

(Try KONAMI code somewhere)
